Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light of summer is the radiance of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the aftermath of the tears lies a live broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the best animation so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully and don't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every Monday at 7 30 P.M...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the find the girl Run Away special!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we'll be broadcasting live from Nengjo Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Run Away areas for the girls tonight are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nengjo Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hamahacho Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kabutobi Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the participants are able to find all of the\Ngirls within thirty minutes, they can win...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Â¥1,000,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be as exciting as last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run Away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't many customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're making any money here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just what they need...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that big hourglass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wanted to make this an appointment place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A thirty-minute hourglass is enormous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How stupid of me, I should've made a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's completely full.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's eat somewhere else then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, how can I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made a reservation for 8:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mean we still have thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food at that restaurant is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't look like a cheap restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's meet here just before 8:00, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, you can roam around freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a mystery bookstore on the second floor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be looking at clothes, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you before 8:00, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, these stairs are closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use the stairs over there, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugar nuts for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving you more tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man was stabbed on the second floor of the Beika shopping mall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:04:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was stabbed from behind, which caused him to fall forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hit his face on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was only stabbed a moment ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means it's highly likely that the culprit is still in the building...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must love these cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe the cases are calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you here as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in that bookstore over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I heard a scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the wallet is still there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to be robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay back, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,End of the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this "Dad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still four girls left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure got here quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Nishiyama Yukio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ambulance is on its way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first eye witness is Yamaguchi Shiori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She claims to be employed at that store over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Koide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the manager of that cosmetics store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a call to headquarters at 19:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you the one who called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,19:30?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, Nishiyama and\NYamamuchi san were always fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's known in this shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always messing with clothes and toys, but never puts them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He breaks a lot in here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always messing with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, he's very unliked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ShioriâI mean, Yamaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}âwasn't\Nalways on good terms with Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude that he used her first name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it goes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just yell it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say I stabbed Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's hated me ever since I broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now he wants to make me a suspect for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone knew that Nishiyama had an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he never messed around in your store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even two days ago, you two were arguing about something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone could hear you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know something about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were paying back money to Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were always fighting with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you have a motive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, may I come through?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The famous detective Mouri Kogorou has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:08:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His pachinko prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why there's no use bringing him anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what were you two doing at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another girls has been found!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only three girls remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time-limit is approaching fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Girls, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the scream on the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And immediately ran to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a lot of time has passed since the criminal stabbed Nishiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other stairs were closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would have to use these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who wants sugar nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have enough for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm not a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were here the entire time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was someone really stabbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone come down the stairs before the scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a few who went upstairs, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, please clear the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to seal the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get everyone back upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the scream, no one went down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it's likely the criminal is still upstairs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal must still be inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, I shall get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this is an assault case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone in or out of this building, no matter the circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been an assault case inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't come in until we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, pal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My boss can get you fired easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His boss must be powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, we need to get in this building immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one enters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasegu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in front of the building, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police won't let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third Run Away girl has been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we're down to two girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go, go! Run Away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't eat dinner now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Koide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cosmetics shop, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stole something from my store again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did I steal something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you check my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager, could you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stealing is a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more girl until Â¥1,000,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can they make it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The display glass with lipstick behind it is in the front of the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, from there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were looking right at the crime scene\Nwhile you were stealing lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you were acting so strange after the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You usually run away immediately after stealing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this time, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you left the building and met the\Ncriminal outside, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you were thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But later, you thought you could escape through the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what was the criminal like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened so fast that I couldn't see what he looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man looked at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was scared, so I closed my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the criminal male and left-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he had the knife in his left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he was wearing a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was black and very thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel so good now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't steal anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Detective{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I searched the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I searched for the weapon and anyone suspicious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else on this floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all that's above are offices and clinics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say the police have already searched up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find a black coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit wore a black coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't get to look in the male's restroom, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police would have searched there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like there are any other places for him to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he stab him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the whole point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman and manager that were\Narguing earlier can't be responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like a revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wallet was there, so it can't be a robbery either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the culprit and victim had been fighting,\Nsomeone would have overheard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems no one did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the culprit's bigger goal wasn't to attack him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As in, if it wasn't revenge, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were two people who called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First we have the manager, Koide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then we have the one who called the police before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably the man in the black coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a call to headquarters at 19:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you the one who called?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone called the police before stabbing Nishiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:17:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a reason for getting the police here as soon as possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They look creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit didn't want those two to get in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used the police to have the building sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the only way to hide a certain something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to hide what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was calling someone inside the building after it was closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he was leaving a voice mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So now we need to find someone inside\Nwho can't answer their cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one that those two want to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the culprit's motive was to prevent them from getting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit's true motive is to attack\Nthe person who was to meet those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the dentist, where your phone has to be turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you match the appointment with the dentist...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And coincide it with the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can close off the entire area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have an appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can wait in line if it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there someone else who's waiting for their appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are other urgent patients...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's one of those three, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:18:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next patient, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come to take revenge for Nobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
