Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's him over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thank all of yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Masuda Taizo, a Diet member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He almost killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you who killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had someone else confess to that accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've looked into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After three months of searching, I found some witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just tell that to the police!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't want to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the opponent is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy has to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not a reason to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, you criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to hear more about this running\Naway from the scene of an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's put a stop to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please drop the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,0!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time has run out with one girl left!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We couldn't give away the Â¥1 000,000 again this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you next week at Beika!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad is gonna treat us to Italian food tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join us, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably the only time Uncle will treat you to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, see, the restaurant is very crowded...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure if they were even open...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you...
