Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
