Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, sorry about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your food, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
